Telson 1.31 times as long as broad, lateral margin bearing 3 spines in the middle third portion, 1 spine in the posterior third portion, posterior margin broadly convex, densely setose with posteromedian spine, posterolateral angle unarmed; dorsal surface with 1 pair of submedian subcircular depressions anteriorly, 2 spines in each oblique row (
